title.narrative: China: Anhui Medium Cities Urban Transport Project

description.narrative: The development objective of the project is to improve mobility on selected main corridors of the municipalities of Anqing, Huaibei, Lu’an and Wuhu in Anhui Province in a safe and efficient manner.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA Section I, para 1 (a)(b)(c)(d) | Description :Anhui shall maintain until project completion (1)AnhuiProvincial Project Leading Group(APLG) (2)Anhui Provincial PMO (APMO) (3) Project City Leading Groups (PCLGs) (4) Project City PMO(PCPMOs) | Frequency :Monthly
Finance Agreement :PA Section I, para 2 | Description :Anhui shall cause each Project City to implement its respective RAP and EMPin a manner satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :Monthly
Finance Agreement :PA Section I, para 3 | Description :Anhui shall cause each Project City not to amend, suspend, abrogate or waiveits respective EMP and RAP. | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :PA Section I, para 5 (a) | Description :Anhui shall cause each Project City to prepare by 12/15 each year, awork plan for their respective part of the project, incl.: activity scope and schedule, financing plan, budget arrangements. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section I, para 5(a) | Description :Prepare a proposed work plan for the carrying out of its respective partof the project during the following calendar year. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section I, para 8 | Description :Anhui shall cause the Project Cities to ensure that the Project is carriedout in accordance with the revisions of the Anti-Corruption Guidelines. | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :PA Section II, para A (1) | Description :Prepare project progress report. Each report covers the period of 1calendar semester and shall be furnished to the Bank no later than 45 days after the end of the period covered by the report. |Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :PA Section II, para A (2) | Description :Prepare mid-term report | Due Date :15-Aug-2013
Finance Agreement :PA Section II, para A (3) | Description :Prepare information to be incorporated into the ICR report | Due Date:30-Oct-2017
